Title of the bachelor topic: Film Lab Management App

Customers can place their orders in 30 minutes time and when the time is over we want to add a finished attribute and change the status of the order as not placed. (modify object definition at run time)
 
Advantages
- can only modifiy the aspects you want
- for legacy code

Disadvantages
- debugging is hard because of the layers
- it gets harder for the garbage collector to deal with it because it creates new memory locations and unrefferenced objects